## File-Specific Requirements

### AI Change Log Comments
If a file contains a comment starting with "AI Change Log:", add a multi-line comment section after it containing:
1. The AI prompt verbatim (for reproducibility)
2. Summary of changes made

### Requirements Comments
If a file contains a comment starting with "Requirements:", update it to properly describe the file's purpose:
- Make it comprehensive, not just one-liners
- Only update if changes actually modify the requirements
- Ensure the description is thorough and explanatory
